  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1004",
  "title": "Range slider throws error when using options.max",
  "body": "I get the following error when trying to set a max value on the rangeSlider widget:\n\n`Uncaught Error: noUiSlider: 'range' value isn't numeric.`\n\nThe configuration is as follows:\n\n``` js\nthis.instantsearch.addWidget(\n    instantsearch.widgets.rangeSlider({\n        container: '#journeys-price-widget',\n        attributeName: 'calculatedPrice',\n        templates: {\n            header: 'Price'\n        },\n        pips: false,\n        max: 30000,\n        tooltips: {\n            format: function(formattedValue) {\n                return 'A' + accounting.formatMoney(formattedValue);\n            }\n        }\n    })\n);\n```\n",
